author: Morgan Phillips
title: State Department responds after Chinese ambassador says it's 'crazy' to blame coronavirus on US military
description: The State Department backed up China’s Ambassador to the U.S. Cui Tiankai for calling the Chinese Foreign Ministry’s coronavirus conspiracy that the U.S. Army was responsible for the virus’ outbreak in Wuhan a “crazy thing.”
